   Business Brief -- Aztar Corp.:
   Court Upholds a Judgment
   Over 1979 Tropicana Deal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/05/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
<CO>
