  2  (2) Merrill Lynch
         Pacific               933      597          64
  3  (3) Japan Fund            801      502          63
  4 (11) 20th Century Select   542      442          81
  5 (32) WPG Tudor Fund        479      402          84
  6  (6) Lindner Fund          586      389          66
  7  (4) Phoenix Growth        618      388          63
  8 (12) G.T. Pacific Growth   540      384          71
